## About SupplySphere

SupplySphere is a blockchain-powered supply chain traceability platform that brings transparency and trust to global trade. From farm to shelf and lab to pharmacy, we ensure every step of a product's journey is securely logged and instantly verifiable.

**Mission**: "Trace it. Trust it. Take it."

**Website**: https://supplysphere.app  
**Documentation**: https://docs.supplysphere.app  
**Community**: https://discord.gg/supplysphere

